name: s_m_load_claimant_stg_from_claimant
description: Session pushed from PC to ICS : s_m_load_claimant_stg_from_claimant

parameters.name: $SQ_claimant$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRCM

runtimeAttrs.Sql Override:
SELECT distinct claimant.SystemId,
                claimant.ParentId,
                claimant.CMMContainer,
                claimant.Id,
                claimant.ClaimantNumber,
                claimant.ClaimantTypeCd,
                claimant.ClaimantSubTypeCd,
                claimant.Comment,
                claimant.StatusCd,
                claimant.StatusDt,
                claimant.InjuryDesc,
                claimant.MajorTraumaCd,
                claimant.FatalityInd,
                claimant.IndexName,
                claimant.PreferredDeliveryMethod,
                claimant.InjuryInvolvedInd,
                claimant.InjuredPartyRelationshipCd,
                claimant.MedicareReportingFilename,
                claimant.ClaimantLinkIdRef,
                claimant.ClaimantLinkDescription,
                claimant.PreferredPaymentMethodCd,
                claimant.InternationalInd,
                claimant.DeathDt,
                claimant.MMIDt,
                claimant.MMIPct,
                claimant.InjuredPartyContacted,
                claimant.NumberOfDependents,
                claimant.NatureCd,
                claimant.BodyPartGeneralCd,
                claimant.BodyPartSpecificCd,
                claimant.BodyPartIAIABCCd,
                claimant.InitialTreatment,
                claimant.DisabilityTypeCd,
                claimant.ClassCd,
                claimant.EmploymentStatusCd,
                claimant.ShiftCd,
                claimant.HourlySalaryCd,
                claimant.AverageWeeklyWagesAmt,
                claimant.HireDt,
                claimant.PayrollLocation,
                claimant.Department,
                claimant.LastWorkedDt,
                claimant.MealsLodging,
                claimant.InpatientOvernight,
                claimant.EmergencyRoomOnly,
                claimant.LiabilityDenied,
                claimant.LiabilityDeniedDesc,
                claimant.PaidFullWages,
                claimant.SalaryContinued,
                claimant.BenefitAmt,
                claimant.DeathBenefitAmt,
                claimant.DaysPaid,
                claimant.WeeksPaid,
                claimant.UpdateCount,
                claimant.UpdateUser,
                claimant.UpdateTimestamp,
                claimant.Status,
                claimant.BenefitRate,
                claimant.OverrideRate,
                claimant.OverrideRateComments,
                claimant.ShortDescription,
                claimant.DetailDescription,
                claimant.OccupationDescription,
                claimant.ManagedCareOrganizationTypeCd,
                claimant.EducationLevel,
                claimant.PreExistingDisabilityCd,
                claimant.ReducedBenefitAmountCd,
                claimant.AdjusterName,
                claimant.AdjusterCompany,
                claimant.AttorneyName,
                claimant.AttorneyFirm,
                claimant.PhoneNamePA,
                claimant.PhoneNumberPA,
                claimant.EmailAddrPA,
                claimant.PhoneNameAttorney,
                claimant.PhoneNumberAttorney,
                claimant.EmailAddrAttorney,
                claimant.AssignedAdjusterName
FROM claimant
where claimant.CMMContainer = 'Claim'
  and claimant.SystemId in (select systemid
                            from advrxxchangedbeans
                            where concat(adddt, addtm) >= '2023-11-20 00:00:00.000'
                              and concat(adddt, addtm) <= '2023-12-02 00:00:00.000'
                              and cmmcontainer = 'Claim') limit 1000;

FROM
  claimant where claimant.CMMContainer='Claim' and claimant.SystemId in (select systemid from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' and
 cmmcontainer='Claim')

parameters.name: $Lkp_provider$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRCM
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT  n.CommercialName as IndexName, 
p.ProviderTypeCd as ProviderTypeCd, p.SystemId as SystemId,p.ProviderNumber as ProviderNumber
FROM 
provider p inner join nameinfo n on
p.systemid=n.systemid
where p.CMMContainer='Provider' 
and n.cmmcontainer='Provider'
and p.ProviderTypeCd='Outside Adjuster'
and n.nametypecd='ProviderName'
